messages.text: It’s 2 in the morning, what’s up ?
And the rain is so strong..
Don’t start scaring me, my parents aren’t here for the weekend
I would like them to pay for my College one day..
My dog has been barking for like 5 minutes
No, It’s cold. I’m good under my blanket haha
Well just turn on the lights and call him.  Lights on reassure me.
I don’t wanna get out of my bed, light is outside my room (weird I know).
All good, I can hear him walking around, must ve been a bird or else
You’re so lucky to have a dog, I would never feel alone
I just have to let my hand on the side and he licks it
I hear a weird dripping sound though
Do you think there could be a leak somewhere ?
I don’t know, just a dripping sound
When something is wrong, he always gets a little nervous, he runs around and stuff
I can bring your breakfast if you want
Talk to you in the morning.
Haha, just in sin with my alarm.
Your dog didn’t drool all over your hand ?
I’m getting in the subway now, I’ll come to your place, cool ?
Where are you, I need you to be here with me
Ok tell me ? What is it ?
This dripping sound would not stop
This is, I can’t even go back to make sure
His blood was dripping on the floor.
I’m in my room now, I’m freaking out, I can’t go back there..
Ok, just relax, I’ll be there soon and we’ll figure this out..
There’s an enveloppe with my name on it on my desk..
Do you think it’s a joke or something ?
Do you wanna wait for me to open it ?
No, I think I’ll open it
If it’s a joke, I’d rather know
BTW, I’m thinking of something rn
You heard the dripping sound last night right ?
Is there something inside the enveloppe
I’m getting out of the house !!!
Ok I’m running in the street now
« If it wasn’t your dog who licked your hand last night, who else ? »
